_sText:
Map made by Zimit

if you upload it to a server please post the ip to me (:

Description: the map is made with a platform you run on with dev textures and three choice of winning over the terrorist there are 17 traps
Trap 1: Doors that catch you and break the floor
Trap 2: 3 Lines Pull you off the path
Trap 3: Choose between 2 doors 2 times and hope you don't die
Trap 4: A short line spins with 1000 in speed
Trap 5: Climb up a ladder and fast get down before getting hit by spikes
Trap 6: You get pushed up on a path and need to hold on the path or you will fall out and in the middle of the path will there come a plate with spikes on and kill you
Trap 7: Is 2 Plates that will smash you into soft meat muhaha :D!
Trap 8: You need to watch out because you need to run or jump fast over the circle with the spinners in the middle if you touch them you die
Trap 9: is a broken television look out for the electricity is still on
Trap 10: A fan pulls you in and you get killed by the spike on the fan.
Trap 11: You getting trapped and a plate will fall down and hit you
Trap 12: You need to run away from the spikes coming from behind better be quick!
Trap 13: The Generic noob box you all now (:
Trap 14: You getting pushed and need to advoid some lasers that when T's click change to different places and could get you killed or lose hp for the next one.
Trap 15: You getting chilled by the vent and move slowly and can't breath for a while
Trap 16 You need to be accurate and jump on the right time to hit the plate there goes forward and backwards all the time and advoid the big X there can show up
Trap 17: FINAL TRAP this trap have 3 traps in one First of them is the standard EXPLOSION. Second of them is some lightning floor and last one is a fan there pulls you and kills you and dissapear one minute after
